divs: Sighting DetailsJune,22,2012 At 10:45 pm, I look NE in the sky and saw a bright object that was simular to a star . It moved ten times faster than an air plane. It did not have the flashing lights as an air plane though. I told my husband to turn around and look but it was taking its time until he turned around it blinked twice, slowed down and the brightness dimmed down . And it disapeared into the night time sky. As the bright object was disapearing the lights were slowy giving out .
